text: Los Irrompibles (English: The Un-breakables) is a 1975 Argentine western movie directed by Emilio Vieyra and starring Jorge Martínez, Ricardo Espalter, Graciela Alfano, Roberto Escalada, Santiago Gómez Cou, Betiana Blum, Enrique Almada, Eduardo D'Angelo. ==Other websites== * Category:1975 movies Category:1970s Western (genre) movies Category:Argentine movies Category:Movies directed by Emilio Vieyra
title: Los Irrompibles
